## Pagination

### Request Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `page` | integer | 1 | Page number (1-indexed) |
| `itemsPerPage` | integer | 25 | Items per page |

Maximum `itemsPerPage`: 100. Requests for more than 100 items per page return a 400 error.

### Response Structure

```json
{
    "items": [...],
    "total": 142,
    "page": 2,
    "itemsPerPage": 25,
    "totalPages": 6
}
```

{% if api_style == "api-platform" %}
API Platform also provides `hydra:view` with `hydra:first`, `hydra:last`, `hydra:previous`, `hydra:next` link relations in JSON-LD responses.

{% endif %}

